commit.message: Removed all files previously committed but now ignored by gitignore

skybox_variable;"

What needs to happen:

Set up slider value as a variable to change star colors, skybox, and
audio.
- Probably best to do the shooting star colors and audio in the slider
behavior script and the main star colors in the star field script.
Merge in Oculus support.
